snippet.title: Monzo: Official Trailer - Google Play
snippet.description:
The digital model kits with a fantastic collection of models from Revell. We have released our ground-breaking mobile app that enables the building, painting, texturing, photo montage and large scale sharing of your creations via social media! Download it now!

Google Play: http://bit.ly/MonzoAndroid
